(591, 1, '2015-06-27 09:11:33', '2015-06-27 02:11:33', 'This simple plastic strap-on chair will look familiar to anyone whos come in contact with one of Fisher-Prices ubiquitous (and beloved) line of booster seats, which are all built along similar lines. This model doesnt boast a padded seat like the Space Saver Highchair, but the toy-filled tray makes it stand out. It entertained our baby long enough to get a meal together, and since the toys arent removable, they cant be dropped or hurled. The tray pulls off easily to reveal a plain white one for serving food (once your childs older, you can completely remove the tray so she can dine on the tabletop with the rest of the family). And since the seat design has no crevices to trap crumbs, cleanup was a breeze.', 'Fisher-Price Discover ''n Grow Busy Baby Booster', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fisher-price-discover-n-grow-busy-baby-booster', '', '', '2015-06-27 09:11:33', '2015-06-27 02:11:33', '', 0, 'http://mommee.org/?p=591', 0, 'post', '', 0),
